      {
        "id": 277522,
        "name": "",
        "username": "reg67",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/reg67/{size}/54198_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-10-19T04:52:04.529Z",
        "cooked": "<p>When selecting “Delete” from the messages menu, users are presented with two options: “Delete for Me” and “Delete for Everyone.” This UI has room for improvement. Users can easily mis-tap, and tapping “Delete for Me” removes the user’s ability to “Delete for Everyone.”</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/8/7/87273a3f2d752c2d3da3638db684f2a9317e9e0a.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/87273a3f2d752c2d3da3638db684f2a9317e9e0a\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/8/7/87273a3f2d752c2d3da3638db684f2a9317e9e0a_2_345x244.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"jhCvbUtt8mQBfgSL86KI2JDpkG6\" width=\"345\" height=\"244\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/8/7/87273a3f2d752c2d3da3638db684f2a9317e9e0a_2_345x244.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/8/7/87273a3f2d752c2d3da3638db684f2a9317e9e0a_2_517x366.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/8/7/87273a3f2d752c2d3da3638db684f2a9317e9e0a_2_690x488.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"362C2A\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1170×830 61.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>The Delete button can be replaced with the “Unsend” button while the message can still be unsent, and the “Delete” button can be omitted.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/f/d/fd855dc73f8d562d6454b0dd1a1e1845e740b99a.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/fd855dc73f8d562d6454b0dd1a1e1845e740b99a\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fd855dc73f8d562d6454b0dd1a1e1845e740b99a_2_294x375.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"AaKxezEwxd25kNott8vkyEm8naO\" width=\"294\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fd855dc73f8d562d6454b0dd1a1e1845e740b99a_2_294x375.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fd855dc73f8d562d6454b0dd1a1e1845e740b99a_2_441x562.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/f/d/fd855dc73f8d562d6454b0dd1a1e1845e740b99a_2_588x750.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"27282C\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">900×1145 61.7 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>In cases where users want to delete messages only for themselves, the “Delete” action can be moved to the “Select” menu, and users should be able to delete or unsend multiple messages in the “Select” menu. There should also be a undo for deletes.</p>\n<p>To distinguish it from “Delete”, the undo send icon should not be the trashcan icon.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/8/3/836af288a6b8e2010d5449e3cd81cbc284062d67.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"iKzGj2ezi4RDE1ePZUCBQN5I4NF\" width=\"40\" height=\"38\"></p>",
