        "created_at": "2025-10-19T05:08:47.046Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Technically, you can’t “unsend“ a message, and I prefer the clear words in Signal compared to the marketing term “unsend“ which makes it sound like you could reliably make the send operation undone.</p>\n<p>Apart from that, I agree there is room for improvement for the reasons/risks you mentioned.</p>",
